rComments: Very good prof. He teaches mostly by going through examples with the class. Tries to keep classes happy with some jokes. Normally shows up to tutorials to help out as well. He can be harsh when you disrupt the class but that is for the better. To further show how good he was, classes were almost full throughout most of the semester.
HIGHLY RECOMMENDED FOR RESEARCH IN ONTOLOGY
One of the most excellent profs in first year. Funny and nice and strict when he needed to be. Just the qualities needed in a prof.
